                        <interp inst="t18790113-name-214" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE BEETLES</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a porter at Mr. Norris's, 245, Old Street—I know 23, Wilson Street—I bought a bookcase, table, and other things from</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. EDMUND</hi> Burke Reeves—it contained a lot of papers and books—he told me to take care of them till he called—I gave them to Mr. James Norris, my employer.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18790113-name-215" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18790113-name-215" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18790113-name-215" type="surname" value="NORRIS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18790113-name-215" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES NORRIS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a furniture dealer, of 245, Old Street—I received some papers from the witness Beetles and handed them to Ashwell.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18790113-name-216" type="witnessName">
