                        <interp inst="t18790113-name-216" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY ASHWELL</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Policeman B</hi> 38). I received a bundle of papers from Norris and handed them to Sergeant Miller.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18790113-name-217" type="witnessName">
